description.raw:
* Added arrow, flight heightmap, and iris model

* add camera visual to iris, remove arrow collision

* add transparency to iris camera visual

* added hoop

* Larger hoop

* Added more flight demo models

* add damping for joints in cessna model.

* adding a small 2d gimbal

* updating model info

* update plugin name

* add imu sensor

* remove decay hack

* tweak params for rotor damping

* update model info and prevent slip drift while on ground

* updates per pull request comments

* backup debug models

* renaming small_2d_gimbal to gimbal_small_2d

* adjust model description. adjust model height so it does not intersect with ground.

* rename iris model name
